    <p>These commands refer to most programs in which you are creating, editing, or deleting text, including Microsoft Word, Excel, and plain text editors such as Atom and Sublime Text. Some of the project-level commands only apply to <a href="https://atom.io/">Atom</a> and <a href="http://www.sublimetext.com/">Sublime Text</a>.</p>

